{"tid":2151182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"與初步確診個案有關　荃灣楊屋道街巿晚上7時關閉消毒清潔","createTime":"2020-08-11T09:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T09:18:11.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a44f86c81eb9767f6e25b4624e799e91401c2efa","tid":2151182,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543085-20200811.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543085-20200811.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=40247d04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543085-20200811.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=26488a4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543085-20200811.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n食環署宣布，因應近日有新型肺炎初步確診個案與楊屋道街巿有關連，街巿今日將提早1小時於晚上7時關閉，進行深層清潔消毒工作。<br />\n<br />\n食環署人員會為街市公用地方及設施進行徹底清潔及消毒，並呼籲街巿的檔戶配合，在各自攤檔範圍進行清潔及消毒。<br />\n<br />\n食環署會在街巿外圍及附近街道進行深層清潔。清潔消毒工作預計約4小時。"}]}